headline: Buildots Appoints Former Senior CBRE and JLL Executive Peter Trollope to Advisory Board
summary: AI construction technology leader Buildots today announced the appointment of Peter Trollope to its advisory board. Trollope has served in senior leadership roles at some of the world's largest construction and real estate companies, most recently as Global Head of Project Management Advisory at CBRE Group, where he led a business unit with over 5,000 staff and USD $1 billion annual turnover.

headline: Office conversions accelerate, but many older buildings face demolition: reports
summary: High vacancy rates have driven building owners to repurpose space, which should help the U.S. office market’s recovery. But high costs and incompatible structural designs remain challenges, CBRE says.
